snippet.textDisplay: For a musician what can be more precious gift than this on the world music day. Being able to sing “Lalon Saiji`s” song on such a big platform like Coke Studio Bangla is a great achievement for me. This platform opens a new door on my musical journey. For this firstly I want to give heartiest thanks to the the magician ARNOB Dada. It would have been really impossible to make it happened without him. Thanks to ADIT Dada for his continuous help and support. Take love Soumyadeep dada and all of the vocals of this song. Specially i wanna thanks to all the musicians who have created such a magical creation( SHOB LOKEY KOY) with their instrumental melody. I am really grateful to all of my Teachers of my musical career. Heartiest love to the multitalented Gousul Alam Shaon Dada. Last But not Least I am really grateful to the entire management team of COCACOLA Bangladesh for making me a part of this magical journey of Coke Studio Bangla. Please keep me in your prayers.বাংলা গানের জয় হোক 🙏 🙏 🙏

snippet.textDisplay: সভ্যতা এর বডি এন্ড ফেইস এক্সপ্রেশন প্রত্যেকটা গানের সাথেই ইনএপ্রোপ্রিয়েট হয় এবং হয়েছে। এটাতে লক্ষ রাখার অনুরোধ রইল। সভ্যতার লিড রুলের গানের জন্য শুভ কামনা,। রুবায়েত এর লিড যেদিন হবে কোক স্টুডিও বাংলাকে হাত জোর অনুরোধ ওর হাসবেন্ড এর সাথে ডুয়ো করাবেন। ওদের ডুয়ো বেস্ট।

snippet.textDisplay:
Ornob and Coke studio Bangla,  all the musicians , artists and people who are behind the scene to re-create such nostalgic songs one after another. If I say I am a big fan of coke studio, that's my confession from the bottom of my heart. Even though my 8 year old son started to listen to all the songs especially Nasek Nasek.. 
Thank you for bringing back the old and folk songs as well as the new one (Chilte Road, fabulous melody and most romantic).. Amazing job guys and love you all. 
I want to listen more and more from coke studio. 
One more thing I have to say, when I listen to reviews from different people across the globe,  I feel proud to be Bangladeshi.
See u guys with a new song.
Honestly speaking this is my first comment in coke studio Bangla even on you tube.
